folder: Midland Avenue & Grimsby Street, Staten Island, NY
text:
Midland Avenue, east side, south from Grimsby to Freeborn Streets. The two-story building, on the right, is occupied by the United Civic League of Midland Beach, Inc.
August, 19, 1935
P.L. Sperr
